=== NEWS ARTICLE ===
Title: 11 IPOs set to list this week. GMPs signal listing returns of up to 90%
Source: Economic Times - Markets
Published: 2025-12-28 06:34
Related Stocks: General Market News
Categories: markets

Summary:
India’s IPO calendar is packed with 11 listings this week, largely dominated by SME issues, even as fresh fundraising momentum slows. Grey market trends signal sharp listing gains in select names, led by E to E Transportation and Shyam Dhani Industries, while most others point to muted or flat debuts amid cautious sentiment.

Sentiment: neutral
